reviewText: Awesome! Okay, I bought this strictly for The Neverending Story 3 but I love all of these movies. My kids weren't as thrilled with King of the Wind and Into the West (must be a sign of the times) but they loved Neverending Story and A Wrinkle in Time. The quality is great, and you can't beat the price!
Great DVD, Purchased for my Daughter's Classroom
wish it had a title page or information about which movies on which sides

It's AWESOME TY. ALL THE MOVIES ARE GREAT MOSTLY NEVERENDING STORY 3. THATS WHY I BOUGHT IT TO END MY COLLECTION BUT OTHER 3 ARE VERY GOOD TO

Finding out a teenaged Jack Black was the bad kid in Neverending Story III was a fun surprise. The rest of the movie is about what youd expect from a third installment in a franchise that gets away from the source material. Havent watched the other movies in the set.
I've only seen 2 of them never ending and into the west . The never ending is always a good story , I'm  big into horse stories  so this was a great story .
